    "An **.srt** file generated by **[SubPlz](https://github.com/kanjieater/SubPlz)** and an audiobook (**.mp3**/**.m4b**) are required.": {
      "comment": "Context: Sasayaki audiobook feature screens. Surrounding UI includes setup instructions, SRT/audio matching, playback controls, command center options, and Sasayaki theme settings. Preserve Markdown and product names.",
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "需要由 **[SubPlz](https://github.com/kanjieater/SubPlz)** 生成的 **.srt** 文件和一本有声书（**.mp3**/**.m4b**）。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
